title: Arsenal accused of lack of respect after leaving non-league Sutton's away changing room in a tip - and they even left milk on the radiator!
text:
EFL messing room Arsenal accused of lack of respect after leaving non-league Sutton’s away changing room in a tip – and they even left milk on the radiator! 
Pictures have emerged of the mess the Gunners left the facilities in after their FA Cup triumph By LEE ASTLEY
